"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-pressbox-press-releases-olympic-and-paralympic-fans-unite-team-usa-and-nbcuniversal-bring-olympic-and-paralympic-games-paris-2024-to-roblox-for-an-immersive-celebration\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Team USA Ultimate Obby\\\" experience on Roblox offers first-ever opportunity to watch Olympic and Paralympic Games highlights and engage with Team USA athlete characters on an online immersive platform July 22, 2024 Colorado Springs, Colo.- With Team USA athletes ready to compete at the Olympic and Paralympic Games Paris 2024 and fans ready to celebrate them in new and exciting ways, the U.S. Olympic & Paralympic Committee and NBCUniversal today invite sports fans and supporters of Team USA to join together in an immersive world on Roblox - with first-ever custom experiences built just for them.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 43, \"end\": 49, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roblox\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roblox\", \"types\": [\"Q7889\", \"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roblox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roblox\"}, {\"begin\": 145, \"end\": 153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999983419912, \"rank\": 1.657316050925839e-09, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 438, \"end\": 450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999636202, \"rank\": 3.596772548483319e-11, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 494, \"end\": 502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999983419912, \"rank\": 1.657316050925839e-09,