_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2552, \"end\": 2557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"score\": 0.9999999896117515, \"rank\": 1.0383131175846574e-08, \"text\": \"House\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\"}, {\"begin\": 2611, \"end\": 2616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.668400959397972e-20, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"real life\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2541}, {\"ngram\": \"the historic Palais Brongniart\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2607}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Roblox, however, Team USA House is a \\\"Vibe House\\\" where fans can meet athletes, play casual games inspired by additional sports, and hang out with friends.\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2650, \"end\": 2656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roblox\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roblox\", \"types\": [\"Q7889\", \"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roblox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roblox\"}, {\"begin\": 2667, \"end\": 2675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999983419912, \"rank\": 1.657316050925839e-09, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2676, \"end\": 2681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"score\": 0.9999999896117515, \"rank\": 1.0383131175846574e-08, \"text\": \"House\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a \