ia.org/resource/Chiaka_Ogbogu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chiaka_Ogbogu\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Official Outfitter\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2841}, {\"ngram\": \"Team USA\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2853}, {\"ngram\": \"a dedicated floor\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2876}, {\"ngram\": \"an immersive brand experience\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 2934}, {\"ngram\": \"dynamic video components\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3019}, {\"ngram\": \"an interactive selfie station\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3053}, {\"ngram\": \"Ralph Lauren-sponsored athletes\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3090}, {\"ngram\": \"Kamren Larsen\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00b7Team USA Athletes- The following 20 Team USA athletes, all of whom collaborated with the USOPC on the character design process, will be featured in the experience as NPCs (non-playable characters): Alise Willoughby BMX Racing Ashleigh Johnson Water Polo Brian Bell Wheelchair Basketball Carissa Moore Surf Chiaka Ogbogu Volleyball CJ Nickolas Taekwondo Evy Leibfarth Canoe / Kayak Ezra Frech Paralympic Track and Field Jagger Eaton Skateboard Jamal Hill Paralympic Swimming Jesse Grupper Climbing Kamren Larsen Cycling Kayla DiCello Gymnastics Minna Stess Skateboarding Nick Mayhugh Paralympic Track and Field Shilese Jones Gymnastics Sunny Choi Breaking Tara Davis-Woodhall Track and Field Tatyana McFadden Paralympic Track and Field Victor Montalvo Breaking \\u00b7Breaking Emotes- Two of the athletes, Sunny Choi and Victor Montalvo, both representing Breaking, which will make its debut at the Olympic Games Paris 2024, have served as the inspiration for a first-of-its-kind set of Emotes - a popular kind of digital item that Roblox users acquire and equip their avatars with.\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 4255, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3167, \"end\": 3175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999983419912, \"rank\": 1.657316050925839e-09, \"text\": \