th the Games in entirely new ways.\\\"\", \"from\": 7160, \"to\": 7327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7234, \"end\": 7242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999983419912, \"rank\": 1.657316050925839e-09, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its-kind\", \"from\": 7175, \"to\": 7183}, {\"ngram\": \"other initiatives\", \"from\": 7207, \"to\": 7224}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 7264, \"to\": 7268}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 7295, \"to\": 7304}, {\"ngram\": \"entirely new ways\", \"from\": 7308, \"to\": 7325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to the Team USA Ultimate Obby, available just for fans in the U.S., the International Olympic Committee has launched an additional experience on Roblox, available for fans globally.\", \"from\": 7331, \"to\": 7524, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7350, \"end\": 7358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999983419912, \"rank\": 1.657316050925839e-09, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 7355, \"end\": 7367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Ultimate\", \"score\": 0.9999916324327315, \"rank\": 8.367637127666082e-06, \"text\": \"USA Ultimate\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Ultimate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Ultimate\"}, {\"begin\": 7415, \"end\": 7446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org