 additional mini\", \"from\": 7735, \"to\": 7758}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 7759, \"to\": 7764}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic sports\", \"from\": 7777, \"to\": 7791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Team USA Ultimate Obby Roblox experience was developed in partnership with Monks, the global, purely digital, unitary operating brand of S4Capital plc.\", \"from\": 7796, \"to\": 7951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7800, \"end\": 7808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999983419912, \"rank\": 1.657316050925839e-09, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 7805, \"end\": 7817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Ultimate\", \"score\": 0.9999916324327315, \"rank\": 8.367637127666082e-06, \"text\": \"USA Ultimate\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Ultimate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Ultimate\"}, {\"begin\": 7823, \"end\": 7829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roblox\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roblox\", \"types\": [\"Q7889\", \"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roblox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roblox\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"partnership\", \"from\": 7858, \"to\": 7869}, {\"ngram\": \"Monks\", \"from\": 7875, \"to\": 7880}, {\"ngram\": \"the global, purely digital, unitary operating brand\", \"from\": 7882, \"to\": 7933}, {\"ngram\": \"S4Capital plc\", \"from\": 7937, \"to\": 7950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With a legacy of innovation and specialized expertise, Monks combines an extraordinary range of global marketing and technology services to accelerate business possibilities and redefine how brands and businesses interact with the world.\", \"from\": 7952, \"to\": 8189, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a legacy\", \"from\": 7957, \"to\": 7965}, {\"ngram\": \"innovation\", \"from\": 7969, \"to\": 7979}, {\"ngram\": \"specialized expertise\", \"from\": 7984, \"to\": 8005}, {\"ngram\": \"Monks\", \"from\": 8007, \"to\": 8012}, {\"ngram\": \"an extraordinary range\", \"from\": 8022, \"to\": 8044}, {\"ngram\": \"global marketing and technology services\", \"from\": 8048, \"to\": 8088}, {\"ngram\": \"business possibilities\", \"from\": 8103, \"to\": 8125}, {\"ngram\": \"brands\", \"from\": 8143, \"to\": 8149}, {\"ngram\": \"businesses\", \"from\": 8154, \"to\": 8164}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 8179, \"to\": 8188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its integration of systems and workflows delivers unfettered content production, scaled experiences, enterprise-grade technology and data science fueled by AI-managed by the industry's best and most diverse digital talent-to help the world's trailblazing companies outmaneuver and outpace their competition.\", \"from\": 8190, \"to\": 8497, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Its integration\", \"from\": 8190, \"to\": 8205}, {\"ngram\": \"systems\", \"from\": 8209, \"to\": 8216}, {\"ngram\": \"workflows\", \"from\": 8221, \"to\": 8230}, {\"ngram\": \"unfettered content production\", \"from\": 8240, \"to\": 8269}, {\"ngram\": \"scaled experiences\", \"from\": 8271, \"to\": 8289}, {\"ngram\": \"enterprise-grade technology and data science\", \"from\": 8291, \"to\": 8335}, {\"ngram\": \"the industry's best and most diverse digital talent\", \"from\": 8360, \"to\": 8411}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's trailblazing companies\", \"from\": 8420, \"to\": 8454}, {\"ngram\": \"their competition\", \"from\": 8479, \"to\": 8496}]}, {\"sentence\": \"About USOPC & Team USA Founded in 1894 and headquartered in Colorado Springs, Colorado, the United States Olympic and Paralympic Committee serves as both the National Olympic Committee and National Paralympic Committee for the United States.\", \"from\": 8501, \"to\": 8743, \"entities\": [{\"begin